DeepL continues to make breakthroughs in neural network technology with the addition of two new languages: <b>Turkish </b>and<b> Indonesian</b>. Together they have nearly 300 million speakers, opening the translator to many&nbsp;new users worldwide! These additions bring our language count to 28, with more than 650 possible translation combinations.&nbsp;
